Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fs42\fad(300,300)}{\move(720,60,720,8)}{\blur3}字幕重校、压制：巴洛克哥特
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.10,0:00:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯先生 我又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.84,0:00:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 怎么不改装得正常点 温莉那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.16,0:00:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么办啊 离伊修巴尔还有好长一段路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.13,0:00:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么怎么办的 只能走呗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.09,0:00:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我倒没事 哥哥你肯定会累死的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.65,0:01:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那怎么办啊 到伊修巴尔又没有铁路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一般的公路也封锁了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.58,0:01:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事到如今又不能让军队送我们去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽说这样没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么说先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}呆站在这种地方伊修巴尔也不会朝我们过来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.82,0:01:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 什么呀 总是那么没计划
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.06,0:01:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人没有什么牺牲的话就什么都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.75,0:01:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了得到什么东西就需要付出同等的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.07,0:01:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那就是炼金术的等价交换原则
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那时我们坚信那就是世界的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6\fn华康雅艺体W6\pos(720,760)\3c&HD3CF9C&\fs70}随川而流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.24,0:03:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看 不是车到山前必有路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么车到山前必有路 只是到了个镇子而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么大一个镇子 总能买到一辆车什么的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.68,0:03:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行啊 我们还是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.88,0:03:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}车之类的人家不会卖给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.12,0:03:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}车到山前必有路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 你为什么总是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}多少考虑一下以后的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.73,0:03:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我正好好地考虑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.40,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哪有考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连我们之后要做的事也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.71,0:03:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.85,0:04:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要做的真的是正确的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.81,0:04:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你想阻止斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们出行的目的是取回原本的身体吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.10,0:04:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以说又怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.61,0:04:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过比起斯卡 我们应该先想办法把人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.09,0:04:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你知道自己在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.11,0:04:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想说的是…是不是还有别的路…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不懂你的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总而言之 你必须再好好考虑一下啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 倒是你该再好好考虑考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.87,0:04:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你太多嘴了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真过分 那么我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该冷静一下脑袋的是哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你够可以的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.08,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道厉害了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.85,0:05:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才不怕你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.95,0:05:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你干嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.47,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.50,0:05:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥为什么总是这样啊 那么固执
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.07,0:05:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才没有固执
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有 如果哥哥直率一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还可以和爸爸商量商量…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.46,0:05:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.42,0:05:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无论发生了什么事 我都不会借助他的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这就是固执啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}烦死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随便你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 书…书牛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.09,0:05:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不不 书虫小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.17,0:06:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫西丝卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.32,0:06:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 温维小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.91,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.15,0:06:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.81,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事 你先说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我有事想跟你商量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.62,0:06:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}跟我?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直在调查
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么休斯中佐 不 准将会死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.81,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯中佐 不 准将的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}叫休斯先生好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}古怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随着调查深入越来越多古怪的事浮出水面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.07,0:06:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知该怎么做才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要告诉我 那种事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.68,0:07:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我无法相信军队中的任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就连那个穆斯唐大佐也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托你 我已经受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果再不跟别人谈谈的话 我 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.83,0:07:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 我知道了 你冷静点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 什么啊 别开玩笑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.31,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 把盐拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是休斯先生让我搜集的资料的抄本
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有这些 是我参考那些资料自己搜集的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.50,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 难道你要我把这些都看一遍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.69,0:08:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对不可能 我想起码得用好几个月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 那么我简略说一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事情是由第五研究所的坍塌事故开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为没有记录 所以我也没法知道当时到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 休斯先生的调查就是从那时开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 你发现了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是 休斯先生在调查关于第五研究所和伊修巴尔内战的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}伊修巴尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这只是我的推测
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}休斯先生或许得知了什么不该知道的重大秘密…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.22,0:08:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了 你别哭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.41,0:08:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你知道自己在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.36,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我当然知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们一定会和那个人碰上
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 真是的 跑到哪儿去…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.49,0:09:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛蒂尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在查阅这些资料的时候 注意到了某个人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}某个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.29,0:09:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朱丽叶·道格拉斯大尉 据说是引起伊修巴尔内乱的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.09,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是很奇怪 这个人在伊修巴尔内乱的两年之前就因事故去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看看这些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这…这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是放在休斯先生的文件夹里 从她的故乡送过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.13,0:09:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去世的时间的确是内乱的两年前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定是搞错什么了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.54,0:09:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如说是记录错误 或者说同名同姓
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}政府和军队的记录都准确无误
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人还在军队里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}墓碑上的碑文显示她在伊修巴尔内乱的两年之前去世
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.17,0:10:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然而 在军队的记录中 她的军籍并没有注销
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还直接参与了伊修巴尔战争
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 现已晋升为大总统的秘书官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.85,0:10:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太奇怪了 本应已死去的人却成了大总统的秘书官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不只是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.74,0:10:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果她还活着的话 至少应该五十多岁了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.92,0:10:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是现在大总统的秘书官朱丽叶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么看都是三十多岁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.93,0:10:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会死 也不会变老 这个人究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}净是些说不通的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.30,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我苦思冥想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}终于想到了一种假设
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}假设?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.02,0:11:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果这个假设成立的话 所有矛盾都迎刃而解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朱丽叶·道格拉斯小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.72,0:11:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想不是的 绝对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.35,0:11:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 如果查明这件事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.17,0:11:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就可以知道是谁杀害了休斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我虽然也勉强算是军人 可只是一个记录员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}朱丽叶小姐是大总统的随从人员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.99,0:11:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就凭我是无论如何也接近不了她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.34,0:11:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也没有法去探明情况
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 用窃听之类的方法进一步调查她 如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}窃听? 是男人要离婚时为了掌握证据而安装的那种东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那种事我做不到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.98,0:12:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.92,0:12:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}窃听
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛蒂尔小姐 你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都跟着你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.98,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想让你告诉我 敌人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}敌人?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是那些黑衣人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.38,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还用说么 我要复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不好意思 我的军服…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不不 总干力气活胳膊会变粗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是要减减肥啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}关于那件事 由我来提交报告…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.72,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.51,0:13:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你认识刚才那两个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前认识的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.72,0:13:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这儿 电话线应该都集中在这座设施里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.77,0:13:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 上着好几把锁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}应该还有多重警报装置 不可能那么容易就进去…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.73,0:13:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这点小事 好说好说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好…好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个人的房间在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中央A馆的103号
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}103 103
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.65,0:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个 好了 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}剩下的就是等待了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.31,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话格利德和罗阿他们保护你就毫无意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.04,0:14:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道我的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可是合成兽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.46,0:14:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经不能作为普通人生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我失去了伙伴和格利德 失去了惟一的容身之处
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}即使这样 复仇也太…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你阻止我也没用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.86,0:14:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我身体的一半是蛇 很固执的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么会…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和斯卡好像
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.51,0:14:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我已经一无所有了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对你来说 他们也是敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.75,0:14:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样的话 我来把他们…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.32,0:14:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不打算帮你复仇 也不打算让你去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为罗阿他们一定也是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.84,0:14:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 所以必须要阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.25,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阻止斯卡 还有玛蒂尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.60,0:15:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.23,0:15:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一旦要找起来还真不容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德华 喂 爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪儿也没见阿尔方斯 发生了什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.12,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那家伙的事我哪知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.16,0:15:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又打架了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是他不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他老嚷着爸爸什么时候回来 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.24,0:15:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真头痛啊 阿尔方斯跑到哪儿去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.78,0:15:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可不知道他在哪儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘁 为什么非得我去…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你好 这里是大总统办公室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.29,0:16:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普通线路来的电话 082线
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请接通
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.63,0:16:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}来了 电话来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哟 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恩维
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.42,0:17:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有急事是禁止使用普通线路的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别那么严厉嘛 不是你让我报告的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.63,0:17:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马上就到北方了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太安静了 我来干点什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.54,0:17:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要按要求完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.04,0:17:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恩维?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.83,0:17:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恩维不是爱德他们说过的人造人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要挂了 我这里有件事必须马上办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们该撤了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.57,0:17:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 刚才的谈话 究竟是说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.57,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过好像是在说什么很危险的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.91,0:18:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要掌握证据看来还要一段时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然即使是窃听也不是轻易就有结果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.54,0:18:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.21,0:18:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怎么会知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个 出了什么事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那个女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.18,0:19:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.33,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}爱德和阿尔的妈妈…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.92,0:19:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}温莉?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是温莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.17,0:19:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们在这里做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.17,0:19:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}外星人?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 我们去伊修巴尔吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.62,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去阻止斯卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你怎么知道我在那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.88,0:20:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你没长进啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打完架后不总是缩在河边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.70,0:20:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.80,0:20:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来要怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有什么怎么办的 只能走呗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要不要坐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}玛蒂尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}阿尔 你认识的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.02,0:20:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.77,0:21:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么 蒙您的好意 请多关照喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.09,0:21:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没关系啊 有困难要互相帮忙 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.26,0:21:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会阻止你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.78,0:21:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么出发喽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.34,0:21:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.67,0:21:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.34,0:21:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哥哥 还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们第一次扭在一起打架的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.94,0:21:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那次我被阿尔暴打的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.16,0:21:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我第一次去河边就是那时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.95,0:21:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是那样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.31,0:21:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在师父那儿的时候你也总是打完架就不见人了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.86,0:21:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果害我得干两人份的活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还因为温莉会嫁给谁而打过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.11,0:22:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有过那种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}钢之炼金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.93,0:23:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第三十九集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.59,0:23:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}东方内战
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.14,0:23:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}斯卡所选择的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.03,0:23:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对我们来说 是一个无法忘怀的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}它的名字叫做里奥尔
